entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You have impressed your new contact. This might end creating more contacts in the future. Kaesii has contacted Lercer with news of your success.
entries.journal_entry_description: Lercer has introduced you to your first spy contact. She is not what you expected. She doesn't look like a spy at all. She looks more at home at a Naboo noble's cotillion. Regardless, she knows what she is looking for, and it doesn't seem that difficult from her description.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Kaesii wants you to enter the White Thranta Shipping company and steal plans for a new prototype military speeder. She told you the plans should be located in the company vehicle repair bay. Look for a computer terminal to download the data from. The guards will not be expecting you, but once detected they will most likely shoot on sight.
entries.task01_comm_message_text: Objective achieved; return to me as soon as possible.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Kaesii has contacted you about your success. Return to her a soon as you can.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: You need to bring the plans back to Kaesii. Hopefully you will be well paid for your work.
